snippet.title: Make a Good Mega Man Level 3 - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
For more updates on the project as it nears release, be sure to check out the official MaGMML Discord Server, Twitter, and Website:
https://discord.gg/7H2mXSPM5p
https://twitter.com/MaGMMLC
https://magmmlcontest.com/

Special thanks to all those who contributed to this trailer: 
Yoshiatom, for the idea of the intro and recording the live footage used for it!
https://www.tumblr.com/yoshiatom

KarakatoDzo, for the amazing artwork of the entry Robot Masters, and helping with the silhouette portion of the trailer!
https://twitter.com/KarakatoDzo
https://www.deviantart.com/karakatodzo

Stone McKnuckle, original and cover musician, for granting permission to use their awesome rendition of "Identity" for this trailer (go support them)!
https://www.youtube.com/@StoneMcKnuckle
